title: DAZ3D 22942 - FWSA Natasha HD for Victoria 7
description:
Details
_____________________________________________________________________________________

Natasha is a high quality character for Victoria 7 for use in DAZ Studio 4.8 and up.

The head and body for Natasha are uniquely custom sculpted in Zbrush, and the skin was created using high quality photo references for depth and detail. She also comes with custom sculpted square nails as well as longer upper lashes that can be dialed to your desired length.

So whether you're looking for a sexy secretary, a feisty young woman, a little cutie pie, or the girl next door, Natasha is perfect for all renders.

Please Note: While Natasha was designed with DAZ Studio 4.8 in mind, and its amazing Iray render engine, she will also work and look great using the 3Delight render engine!

_____________________________________________________________________________________
